pageContext.claim: “We have a phony press. We don't have freedom of the press in this country. We have a phony press. They’re dishonest, most of them. We have some fine people from -- fine journalists and reporters and companies. But most of them are fake and phony. CNN, NBC, ABC, CBS, The Washington Post, New York Times -- these are fake papers.”
pageContext.analysis: The news organizations named by Trump are not phony and are not fake. He just does not like to see critical or skeptical news coverage.
